# Migrate from SDK 51 / 52 / 53 / 54 to SDK 55

The full SDK 55 release notes are at https://expo.dev/changelog/sdk-55. This rule covers the LLM-actionable diffs.

## 1. Bump expo and align bundled modules

```sh
npx expo install expo@~55.0.0
npx expo install --fix
```

`--fix` reads `node_modules/expo/bundledNativeModules.json` and updates every bundled module (react-native, react, expo-router, react-native-reanimated, react-native-worklets, react-native-gesture-handler, @shopify/flash-list, expo-camera, expo-file-system, expo-video, expo-audio, etc.) to its SDK 55-matched version.

Source: https://github.com/expo/expo/blob/sdk-55/packages/expo/bundledNativeModules.json

## 2. Babel: worklets plugin

Reanimated 4 moved the Babel plugin to `react-native-worklets`.

```diff
// babel.config.js
 module.exports = function (api) {
   api.cache(true);
   return {
     presets: ["babel-preset-expo"],
-    plugins: ["react-native-reanimated/plugin"],
+    plugins: ["react-native-worklets/plugin"], // must be last
   };
 };
```

See anti-pattern #10.

## 3. FlashList: v1 -> v2

```diff
-<FlashList data={items} estimatedItemSize={64} renderItem={...} />
+<FlashList data={items} renderItem={...} keyExtractor={(i) => i.id} />
```

Remove `estimatedItemSize`, `estimatedFirstItemOffset`. For mixed item types, add `getItemType`. See anti-patterns #23, #32.

## 4. expo-file-system: classic -> new API

The default export is now the `File`/`Directory` API. Choose one of:

A. Migrate to the new API:

```diff
-import * as FileSystem from "expo-file-system";
-await FileSystem.writeAsStringAsync(FileSystem.documentDirectory + "x.txt", "hi");
+import { File, Paths } from "expo-file-system";
+const file = new File(Paths.document, "x.txt");
+await file.write("hi");
```

B. Defer migration by importing the legacy export explicitly:

```diff
-import * as FileSystem from "expo-file-system";
+import * as FileSystem from "expo-file-system/legacy";
```

See anti-pattern #24.

## 5. expo-av: split into expo-video and expo-audio

```diff
-import { Video, Audio } from "expo-av";
+import { useVideoPlayer, VideoView } from "expo-video";
+import { useAudioPlayer } from "expo-audio";
```

Rewrite call sites. `expo-av` is removed from Expo Go in SDK 55.

```sh
npx expo install expo-video expo-audio
npm uninstall expo-av
```

See anti-pattern #25.

## 6. Drop newArchEnabled / jsEngine

```diff
 {
   "expo": {
-    "newArchEnabled": true,
-    "jsEngine": "hermes",
     ...
   }
 }
```

Legacy Architecture is removed in SDK 55. Hermes has been the default since SDK 49. See anti-patterns #38, #39.

## 7. runtimeVersion: string -> fingerprint policy

```diff
 {
   "expo": {
-    "runtimeVersion": "1.0.0",
+    "runtimeVersion": { "policy": "fingerprint" },
   }
 }
```

See anti-pattern #17.

## 8. expo-cli -> npx expo + eas

```diff
 "scripts": {
-  "start": "expo start",
-  "android": "expo run:android",
-  "build:android": "expo build:android"
+  "start": "npx expo start",
+  "android": "npx expo run:android",
+  "build:android": "eas build -p android --profile production"
 }
```

And remove `"expo-cli": "^6.0.0"` from `dependencies`. See anti-pattern #12.

## 9. Migrate Camera, useAnimatedGestureHandler, expo-permissions

If you are still on SDK 51, you may also need:

- `Camera` from `expo-camera` -> `CameraView` (anti-pattern #6)
- `useAnimatedGestureHandler` -> `GestureDetector` + `Gesture.Pan` (anti-pattern #5)
- `expo-permissions` -> per-module APIs (anti-pattern #20)
- `react-native-fast-image` -> `expo-image` (anti-pattern #28)
- `react-native-vector-icons` -> `@expo/vector-icons` (anti-pattern #37)
- `react-native-fs` -> `expo-file-system` (anti-pattern #36)

## 10. Verify and publish

```sh
npx expo-doctor
npx tsc --noEmit
eas build -p ios --profile preview
eas update --auto
```

`expo-doctor` flags remaining mismatched versions and missing config plugin entries.

Source: https://docs.expo.dev/upgrading-expo-sdk-walkthrough/
